The Davis Dog Owners Group works with the City of Davis Parks & Community Services Department on dog related matters in the city. They organize events at the Toad Hollow Dog Park and other dog areas. They have a wiki website at davisdogs.org, a Yahoo group mailing list called http://pets.groups.yahoo.com/group/davisdogpark/ davisdogpark and also use the email address MailTo(davisdogpark AT yahoo DOT com). Messages of the Yahoo group are only viewable by group members, and All membership requests for davisdogpark need to be approved by the moderator.
